bits_fields.description:
When RB_BAT_MON_EN=0, set the high precision ultra-low voltage and low voltage detection threshold: (ultra-low voltage reference threshold, low voltage reference threshold)
00: 1.7V, 1.95V;
01: 1.9V, 2.15V;
10: 2.1V, 2.35V;
11: 2.3V, 2.55V.
When RB_BAT_MON_EN=1, take RB_BAT_LOW_VTHX as the highest bit, adding these 2 bits, these 3 bits are used to set the low-power low-voltage monitoring threshold:
000: 1.7V;
001: 1.8V;
010: 1.9V;
011: 2.0V;
100: 2.1V;
101: 2.2V;
110: 2.3V;
111: 2.4V.

RTC timing mode fixed cycle (timing) selection:
000: 0.125S; 001: 0.25S; 010: 0.5S; 011: 1S;
100: 2S; 101: 4S; 110: 8S; 111: 16S.
